snippet.textDisplay:
An apt song in the edit for someone who has had to fight a lone battle .
Par woh jo haunsla aur vishwas rakhta hai usse har parasthiti mein positive hona hai.
Aap jaise young people hai na jo bina bhaddi language use kare Manisha ka saath dete hain.Uspar Bhagwan ki kripa hai jo aap sab ka support hai,hamesha karte rehna,also always tell her right from wrong.Jisse aap dil se maante hai usko hamesha sahi raste par hi daalte hain.God bless you.
